## Summary: What Makes This 10x

| Existing Systems (Increff/Toolio) | KYROS v2 |
|---|---|
| Allocate by formula, show results | **Judge its own decisions before showing results** |
| Same depth for all stores | **Depth-first: concentrate where it matters** |
| No confidence measure | **Decomposed confidence with evolution projection** |
| Manual review required | **System says APPROVE/CAUTION/REJECT with reasons** |
| Static allocation | **Self-improving: cold-start → data-rich automatically** |
| Dashboards for interpretation | **Decisions for action** |
